r own feeling and those of others, for motivating ourselves, and for managing emotions well in ourselves and in our relationships. In a sense we have brain, two minds and two different kinds of intelligence, rational and emotional\r\nGoleman','','-','Manoj Kumar Singh','143-146','NO','-','International Journal of Education and Information Sciences','26','32','2013-07-23 17:36:30','e',11,'','',NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'subscription',NULL),(580,'A Study of Adjustment of Principals of  Secondary  Schools','It can be said that in all systems of formal education, the Principal holds a key position. The success and effectiveness of the system largely depends upon his performance. There is a lot of differences in rural and urban culture adjustment of the boys & girls and their culture. Their education is also different in a lot of cases. Their study centers have different facilities for them. So their educational interest are so different. According to their climate the schools Principals also adjust their life style. This paper is concerned with the study of adjustment of Principals of Secondary schools.','','-','Mohammad Zahid and Sandhaya Gihar','147-152','NO','-','International Journal of Education and Information Sciences','26','32','2013-07-23 17:36:30','e',11,'','',NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'subscription',NULL),(583,'ch-,M+ Lrj ds vkoklh; ,oa xSj&vkoklh; fo|kfFkZ;ksa ds kSf{kd ruko dk rqyukRed v/;;u','ruko O;fDr ds fy;s ,d ,slh vkarfjd ;k ckgjh fLFkfr gS tks mlds lkekU; O;ogkj dks izHkkfor djrh gS vkSj O;fDr dks mldk lkeuk djus ds fy, izsfjr vkSj ck/; djrh gSA fdUgha dkj.kksa ls O;fDr bu fLFkfr;ksa dk lkeuk ugha dj ikrk gS rks ruko gksrk gSA izLrqr v/;;u esa ch-,M+ Lrj ds vkoklh; ,oa xSj&vkoklh; fo|kfFkZ;ksa ds kSf{kd ruko dk rqyukRed v/;;u fd;k x;k gSA ftles izfrnkZ gsrw] gfj;k.kk jkT; ds vEckyk tuin ds ch0,M0 egkfo|ky;ksa ds 200 fo|kfFkZ;ksa dks kkfey fd;k x;k A bu 200 fo|kfFkZ;ksa esa ls lkS vkoklh; 50 yM+ds vkSj 50 yM+fd;k gSa vkSj lkS xSj&vkoklh; 50 yM+ds vkSj 5