s. They study the demand patterns and the market trends and work out the lowest price that they can offer to attract a huge section of the consumers while still maintaining a profitable margin. As the Indian market is price-oriented, the domestic players are slowly losing their share to the strategic Chinese entrepreneurs. \r\nThe only way the above problem can be solved up to an extent is by introducing SME favourable policies. The Indian Government should understand the basic fact that SMEs are the backbone of Indian economy and their growth will in turn add to the development of India. Indian SMEs should also continuously study the market needs and come up with innovative and cost effective products to tackle the burning issue. Because of cheaper prices products made in China are becoming more popular among the Indian masses. This has had a very negative effect on our own manufacturing units and as a result ma','','Impact, Chinese Products, Reform and Suggestions',' Naveen Singh  T. K. Sharma',' 105-115','NO','','International Journal of Education and Information Sciences','31','45','2013-07-23 17:36:30','E',11,'','',NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'subscription',NULL),(983,' Abraham Lincolns First Inaugural Address: Though Unsuccessful While exhibited his Education and Humility ','Abraham Lincoln chose to draw on four historic documents for his speech: the United States Constitution, Daniel Websters reply to Robert Y. Hayne, Andrew Jacksons Nullification Proclamation, and Henry Clays compromise speech of 1850. He chose these because each dealt in some way with states rights, the premier issue of the day. He assured Confederate states in his speech that he\'s not going to interfere with the institution of slavery. He held that the federal government was prevented by the Constitution from banning slavery in states where it already existed. Confederate states shouldn\'t fear him for that reason. Second That the south can\'t leave the Union and get away with it! He was trying to allay the fears and placate the of Southerners, the speech did not dissuade them from starting the war, which they initiated the following month. ','','Inaugural, Union,  slaves, Republican Party, Confederates, Civil War, Civil War, United States ','  S. K. Singh , Prachi  ',' 117-120  ','NO','','International Journal of Education and Information Sciences','31','45','2013-07-23 17:36:30','E',11,'','',NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'subscription',NULL),(984,' mPp fk{kk esa lwpuk izkS|ksfxdh dk ;ksxnku','      Hkkjr gh ugha foo ds vusd nsskksa esa kS{kf.kd Vhoh dk;Ze izlkfjr gksrs gSA^ baXySM] tkiku vkSj la;qDr jkT; vesfjdk esa fodflr kS{kf.kd Vsyhfotu lsok miyC/k gS] fczfVk vksiu ;wfuoflZVh vius fofHkUu ladk;ksa ds dk;Zeksa ds Vhoh izlkj.k gsrw chchlh ij Vhoh Vkbe dk Hkjiwj mi;ksx djrk gSA la;qDr jkT; vesfjdk ljdkjh Vsyhfotu ij Ldwy dk;Ze d{kk vkSj ?kj nksuksa esa fk{kdksa vkSj Nk=ksa dks mi;ksxh dk;Ze miyC/k djkrk gSA','','Vhoh dk;Ze, vksiu ;wfuoflZVh ',' eerk HkkfV;k  lqkek xka/kh',' 121-126','NO','','International Journal of Education and Information Sciences','31','45','2013-07-23 17:36:30','H',11,'','',NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'subscription',NULL),(985,' fk{kk ds mn~ns; dks xfr nsrk jsfM;ks','      izlkj.k dk eq[; mn~ns; gS lwpuk] fk{kk vkSj eukasjtuA izlkj.k ,d lkekftd izf;k gS vkSj lEizsk.k mldk eq[; y{; gSA izlkj.k ,d dyk gS vkSj vfHkO;fDr esa dkSk.k mldh vfuok;Z ;ksX;rk gSA izlkj.k dh ,d eq[; fokskrk mldh jpuk/kfeZrk gSA jpuk/kfeZrk dk vFkZ ekuoh; izfrHkk ds mi;ksx ls ,d fofkB l`tu ;k fofp=rk dk mRiknu djuk gSA^ fk{kk ds {ks= esa tgka jsfM;ksa dk Hkjiwj mi;ksx gks jgk gS vkSj mPp fk{kk ds {ks= esa dgk tk ldrk gS fd jsfM;ksa vius mn~ns; esa lQy gS','','fk{kk, jsfM;ks, vkdkkok.kh ',' eerk HkkfV;k  lqkek xka/kh',' 127-131','NO','','International Journal of Education and Information Sciences','31','45','2013-07-23 17:36:30','H',11,'','',NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'subscription',NULL),(986,' A Comparative Study of Role Conflict and Professional Commitment among th