 G., Noh, K. Y., &amp; Ryu, K. H. (2007, May). Mining biosignal data: coronary artery disease diagnosis using linear and nonlinear features of HRV. In&nbsp;Pacific-Asia Conference on Knowledge Discovery and Data Mining&nbsp;(pp. 218-228). Berlin, Heidelberg: Springer Berlin Heidelberg.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Guru, N., Dahiya, A., &amp; Rajpal, N. (2007). Decision support system for heart disease diagnosis using neural network.&nbsp;Delhi Business Review,&nbsp;8(1), 99-101.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Parthiban, L., &amp; Subramanian, R. (2008). Intelligent heart disease prediction system using CANFIS and genetic algorithm.&nbsp;International Journal of Biological, Biomedical and Medical Sciences,&nbsp;3(3).</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Saraogi, V. K., Matolia, D. K., Kumar, J., Saini, M. K., &amp; Malik, A. K. (2023, June). Importance of WPA3 in fog computing. In&nbsp;AIP Conference Proceedings&nbsp;(Vol. 2782, No. 1). AIP Publishing.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','. ','  Arvind Kumar Shukla*, C. K. Singh ',' 85-90  ','YES','2023-2-2-P3.pdf','International Journal of Science and Engineering','92','145','2026-02-17 16:47:49','E',10,'arvind.ecimt@gmail.com',' Department of Computer Science, Nehru Gram Bharti (Deemed to be) University, Prayagraj, Uttar Prade',' https://doi.org/10.58517/IJSE.2023.2203 ','pending',NULL,NULL,'open',NULL),(1515,' REVIEW OF HISTORY OF INDIAN MATHEMATICS','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	The purpose and value of mathematics have been a pursuit for thousands of years and have</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	always been valued for its ability to provide knowledge and understanding in various civilizations. The</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	chapter explores the development of mathematics in various cultures and the importance of written</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	documents in understanding mathematical practices. The distinction between pure and applied</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	mathematics is also highlighted, with industry and government funding research in mathematics for</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	practical applications. The motivations for becoming a mathematician, whether for personal fulfilment</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	or societal impact, are also examined. The chapters explore the intersection of mathematics with everyday</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	life, education, and professional fields, shedding light on the different perspectives on the value and</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	importance of mathematical in society.</div>\r\n','<div>\r\n	Agargiin, Ahmet G.; Fletcher, Colin R., 1994. &ldquo;Al-Farisi and the fundamental Theorem of</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	arithmetic,&rdquo; Historia Mathematica, 21, No. 2, 162-173.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull; Allman, George Johnston, 1889. Greek Geometry from Thales to Euclid, Longmans, Green &amp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Co., London.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull; Amir-Moez, Ali R., 1959. &ldquo;Discussion of difficulties in Euclid by Omar ibn Abrahim Al-</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Khayyami,&rdquo; Scripta Mathematica, XXIV, 275-303.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull; Amir-Moez, Ali R., 1963. &ldquo;A paper of Omar Khayyam,&rdquo; Scripta Mathematica, XXVI, No. 4, 323-</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	337.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull; Andrews, George E., 1979. &ldquo;An introduction to Ramanujan&rsquo;s &lsquo;lost&rsquo; notebook,&rdquo; American Mathematical Monthly, 86, No. 2, 89-108.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull; Ang Tian-Se; Swetz, Frank J., 1986. &ldquo;A Chinese mathematical classic of the third Century: The Sea Island Mathematical Manual of Liu Hui, Historia Mathematica, 1 3, No. 2, 99-117.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull; Aschbacher, Michael, 1981. &ldquo;The classification of the finite simple groups,&rdquo; The 